     H            Y.
      ****************************************************************
      *  PROGRAM    : AFFR17                                         *
      *  WRITTEN    : 02/13/2023                                     *
      *  WRITTEN BY : LEC                                            *
      *  FUNCTION   : UPDATE NAPCK DELIV ROUTE/BIN SCHEDULE          *
      *               FROM UPLOAD                                    *
      ****************************************************************
     FAB#PP89 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           INSURT  9
     C                     PARM           INSHDT  8
     C                     PARM           INHOME  1
      *
     C           K#891     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           INHOME
     C                     KFLD           SHID
      *
     C           K#892     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           INHOME
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *
     C                     TIME           WSDT
     C                     MOVELINSHDT    SHID    80
      *
     C           SHID      IFNE *ZERO
      *
     C           K#891     SETGTAB#PP89
     C           K#892     REDPEAB#PP89                  98
      *
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C           A9SURT    ANDNEINSURT
     C           *IN98     OREQ *ON
     C                     CLEARAB#PP891
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     A9KODT
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       A9KOTM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     A9KOME
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      A9UPGM
     C                     MOVEL#WSID     A9UPWS
     C                     Z-ADDSHID      A9FRDT
     C                     MOVELINHOME    A9HOME
     C                     MOVELINSURT    A9SURT
     C                     WRITEAB#PP891
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *------------------------------------------------------
